sentences: Justin Putuhena (born 12 May 1986), better known by his stage name Justin Prime, is a Dutch progressive and electro house DJ and record producer.
He is a sound engineer graduate and began his music career in 2001 producing techno and hardstyle music.
He released Cannonball with Showtek in 2012 and received a platinum-plated record plus two golden records for this track.
